# CODEOWNERS — the immutable control plane (HG-0002)
#
# ADOPT: replace @your-org/platform-admins with a REAL team the agent's identity is NOT a
# member of. Until you do, `scripts/control-plane-check.mjs` FAILS on the placeholder by
# design — a copied-but-never-adopted template must not read as a green control.
# This file is what makes "the agent cannot edit its own guardrails" true: every
# path below requires a Code Owner review before merge, enforced by branch protection (see
# governance/activation-runbook.md). `scripts/control-plane-check.mjs` fails CI if any of
# these paths loses its owner — the paper control and the check are defence in depth.
#
# Last match wins. Keep the control-plane rules LAST so nothing later un-owns them.

# Sensible default owner for the whole repo (optional — remove if you prefer explicit-only).
*                                       @your-org/engineering

# --- Control plane: hooks, gates, workflows, settings, governance data, and CODEOWNERS itself ---
/.claude/hooks/                         @your-org/platform-admins
/.claude/settings.json                  @your-org/platform-admins
/.claude/agents/                        @your-org/platform-admins
/discovery/gates/                       @your-org/platform-admins
/discovery/render/                      @your-org/platform-admins
/scripts/discovery-link-check.mjs       @your-org/platform-admins
/scripts/control-plane-check.mjs        @your-org/platform-admins
/.github/workflows/                     @your-org/platform-admins
/docs/governance/                       @your-org/platform-admins
/CODEOWNERS                             @your-org/platform-admins
